'''美国人口普查'''是在美國施行的[[人口普查|人口普查]]，每10年舉行一次。[[美國革命|美國革命]]后的第一次人口普查是在1790年，由[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]][[托马斯·杰斐逊|托马斯·杰斐逊]]負責實施。<ref name="decennial">{{Cite web|title=Decennial Census – History – U.S. Census Bureau|url=https://www.census.gov/history/www/programs/demographic/decennial_census.html|accessdate=2015-03-19|date=|publisher=Census.gov|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422171352/https://www.census.gov/history/www/programs/demographic/decennial_census.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>每次人口普查結束後，[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]各州的的席位要重新分配，[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]和美國各州的立法機構的選區也要重新劃分<ref>{{cite news |title=人口普查基本知识 ：您需要了解的信息 |url=https://www.census.gov/content/dam/Census/library/factsheets/2019/dec/2020-census101-simplified-chinese.pdf |publisher=美国普查局 |accessdate=2020-11-16 |archive-date=2021-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327004450/https://www.census.gov/content/dam/Census/library/factsheets/2019/dec/2020-census101-simplified-chinese.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，各州的[[選舉人票|選舉人票]]也要重新調整<ref>{{cite news |title=美国大选解读：选票如何计算？选举人制度如何运作？ |url=https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2020-11-06/explainer-election-colledge-in-us-election/12857128 |publisher=澳大利亞廣播公司 |accessdate=2020-11-16 |archive-date=2020-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225015611/https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2020-11-06/explainer-election-colledge-in-us-election/12857128 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

